g 1979</a></div><div class="HomeNewsSlider-item" style="width: 272px"><a class="title" href="/vn/su-kien/tin-moi-nhat-nam-apec-viet-nam-2017-356944.html">Năm APEC Việt Nam 2017</a></div></div></div><div class="HomeNewsSlider-button"><a class="btnNext" href="#" style="display: inline;"> ◄ </a><a class="btnPrev" href="#" style="display: inline;"> ► </a></div></div></div></div></div><vnn xmlns:UIXsltUtils="UserInterface:XsltUtils"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="http://res.vietnamnet.vn/resources.cssx?alias=vietnamnet-standard-detail-v4&amp;version=1.4.5" /><script src="http://res.vietnamnet.vn/resources.jsx?alias=vietnamnet-standard-detail-v4&amp;version=1.4.5"> </script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="http://res.i-vietnam.vn/deploy/s/css/style-1-0-2.css" /><script language="javascript" src="http://res.i-vietnam.vn/resources.jsx?alias=fmsid-standard&amp;version=1.1.5"> </script><vnn xmlns:UIXsltUtils="UserInterface:XsltUtils"><div class="Main-Body DetailPage w-1000"><div class="HomeBlock clearfix"><div class="w-500 left m-r-10"><div class="HomeBlockLeft left"><vnn xmlns:UIXsltUtils="UserInterface:XsltUtils"><div class="clearfix HeadCateBG"><div class="CateTitle left"><a href="/vn/tuanvietnam/" class="Name f-14 bold">TuanVietNam</a></div><span class="subcate  f-n f-14  m-l-5 left">
